dmv.spring.demo.model.entity

Class Role

  • java.lang.Object
    • dmv.spring.demo.model.entity.Role
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RoleApiDocs, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomGrantedAuthority

    public class Role
extends Object
implements RoleApiDocs, Serializable
    Role entity POJO. What system access rights some user has: Administrator or User or whatever.

    This object has Validation restrictions on how many characters can be used to represent the Short and the Full names. Although these constraints are not checked upon setting and not guaranteed upon getting those fields.

    dmv
